headline: Jack Henry & Associates: Shares Aren't As Cheap As I Would Like Them To Be
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc. delivered strong Q4 and FY2025 results, exceeding analyst expectations in revenue, EPS, and adjusted EPS. Read why JKHY is a Hold.
